<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.1">
<l>kuṉṟa moṉṟeṭut tēnti māmaḻai</l>
<l>yaṉṟu kāttavam māṉa rakkarai</l>
<l>veṉṟa villiyār vīra mēkolō</l>
<l>teṉṟal vantutī vīcu meṉceykēṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What [about] the heroism of the archer who conquered the demons,</l>
<l>The lord who, having taken and held up a mountain,</l>
<l>Guarded against the great deluge that day?</l>
<l>The southern breeze comes and blows [like] fire! What do I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
